Get ready for Engineers' Week! From Feb 8th through Feb 12th, the Engineering Student Council will be hosting a week-long series of events through Hop-In, and giving away $3000 of raffle prizes! 

From our Google Career Panel to our Club Demo, E-Week will take you inside the magic behind Berkeley Engineering and the technologies that bring the impossible to reality. Ready to experience the magic Register and attend events through Hop-In:

To attend any of the events, you must pre-register for the days you would like to attend - the full programming schedule can be found in the registration links:

- Events from Monday (2/8) - Wednesday (2/10): https://hopin.com/events/eweek2021-p1
- Events from Thursday (2/11) - Friday (2/12): https://hopin.com/events/eweek2021-p2

For every event you attend, your name will be entered in our E-ball Raffle on Friday, 2/12. The more events you attend, the more times your name will be entered! Some items that will be raffled off include: Apple iPad, Apple AirPods, Hydroflasks, Amazon Alexas, Beats Headphones, and various gift cards. Starbucks gift cards will also be raffled off after each event.

If you have any further inquiries, please contact: eweek@esc.berkeley.edu or message this Facebook page.

“Any sufficiently advanced technology is indistinguishable from magic.” - Arthur C. Clarke
